---
title: American-Style BBQ Chicken with Wedges, Rainbow Slaw & Corn Cobs
description: Eat the rainbow with this tasty mix of all-American flavours. Tender chicken gets a lightly spiced and saucy coating, with potato wedges, simple corn and a zesty slaw to round out the meal. It's a taste of an American BBQ right in your own home!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/american-style-bbq-chicken-7c9925e8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/american-style-bbq-chicken-5fc9bbac1a794e56eb0e43c8-165bca4c.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/american-style-bbq-chicken-5fc9bbac1a794e56eb0e43c8
